     models, multi-modal models, or other machine-learning systems.

  2. Generation of embeddings, vector representations, or similar
     derivative artifacts that are intended for ingestion into commercial
     retrieval-augmented generation (RAG) systems, vector databases, or
     similar inference pipelines.

  3. Construction of synthetic-data pipelines, alignment datasets,
     evaluation benchmarks, or any dataset offered for sale, sublicense,
     or paid access.

  4. Bulk programmatic crawling, scraping, mirroring, or archival
     beyond what is strictly necessary for direct human reading by an
